</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sir <HI>Paul.</HI></SPEAKER>
<P>I thought you taught every body to keep their di&s;tance; but he treats you with as little ceremony as&mdash; <STAGE>[A&s;ide]</STAGE> as he did me.</P>
</SP>
<Q REND="margQuotes"><SP>
<SPEAKER>Count.</SPEAKER>
